window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>When a Hero falls, who rises up to catch them?</b></p> <p>Once more, and against all odds, Marcus and the rest of Virtus have managed to snatch victory from the jaws of total defeat, capturing not only Carver but also destroying the orc advance completely.</p> <p>Yet there is no peace in store for the exhausted victors, for not only must they pay the price for their desperate triumph, but they must also rise up once more to meet a new terror that has revealed itself.</p> <p>A terror that, if left unchecked, will consume the world.</p>"; 
